Package project.game.player

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FailCountProperty
    This class takes care of the players current failCount (Number of times they've failed in a minigame).
    Player
    This class takes care of the Players Data.
    PlayerProgressManager
    This class keeps track of the players progress and whether or not they have collected an item.
    Settings
    This class keeps track of the configurable settings in the game by enum constants of language and theme.
    SettingsManager
    This class is included in a Player instance and will save the current chosen language, the theme and their preferred volume of sound effects and background music.
